import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import Content from "../../../layout/content/Content"; import Head from "../../../layout/head/Head"; import LogoDark from "../../../images/logo-dark.png"; import { BlockHead, BlockTitle, Button, Icon, BlockDes, BlockHeadContent, Block, BlockBetween, } from "../../../components/Component"; import { invoiceData } from "./Invoice"; import { useParams, Link } from "react-router-dom"; const InvoiceDetails = () => { const [data] = useState(invoiceData); const [user, setUser] = useState(); let { invoiceId } = useParams(); useEffect(() => { const id = invoiceId; if (id !== undefined || null || "") { let spUser = data.find((item) => item.id === Number(id)); setUser(spUser); } else { setUser(data[0]); } }, [invoiceId, data]); return ( {user && ( Invoice #{user.orderId}
  • Created At: {user.date}
Invoice To

{user.name}

  • House #65, 4328 Marion Street
    Newbury, VT 05051
  • {user.phone}

Invoice

  • Invoice ID:{user.orderId}
  • Date:{user.date.split(",")[0]}
Item ID Description Price Qty Amount
24108054 Dashlite - Conceptual App Dashboard - Regular License ${user.invoiceItem1} 1 ${user.invoiceItem1}
24108054 24 months premium support ${user.invoiceItem2} 1 ${user.invoiceItem2}
23604094 Invest Management Dashboard - Regular License ${user.invoiceItem3} 1 ${user.invoiceItem3}
23604094 6 months premium support ${user.invoiceItem4} 1 ${user.invoiceItem4}
Subtotal $ {Number(user.invoiceItem1) + Number(user.invoiceItem2) + Number(user.invoiceItem3) + Number(user.invoiceItem4) + ".00"}
Processing fee $10.00
TAX $50.00
Grand Total ${user.totalAmount}
Invoice was created on a computer and is valid without the signature and seal.
)} ); }; export default InvoiceDetails;
